Mouth is full bod, rich, thick, and heavy, decent carb, very mild warming booze. 
Overall hard to decide, very good, the great characters of the original like coffee vanilla and cocoa are muted a bit due to the rum, but the rum adds it's own awesome character, nicely blended, so hard to compare. Both so delicious though. 1,823 charactersjlindros, Nov 11, 2013
